query:
SELECT lm.id, lm.title, lm.subjectId, lm.userId, s.name as subjectName
FROM learning_modules lm
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON lm.subjectId = s.id
WHERE lm.subjectId = 1
LIMIT 10;
